LunchStart: ^<color=#ffffffff>More odd questions for this odd class.
^<color=#ffffffff>Cherry calls from the other side of the room, waving her arms frantically to get your attention.
^<color=#ffffffff>Oh gosh, you can't suffer to spend time with her. This is your only chance!
^<color=#ffffffff>You had everything you needed, but if she comes over, it's all over.
^<color=#ffffffff>You need to leave, to find a place where she won't follow you.
^<color=#ffffffff>The men's bathroom! Quick! Leave before she catches you!
